# Design System Enforcement

## Build Order

1. Reuse existing primitives in `src/components/ui/`
2. Reuse existing wrappers in `src/components/`
3. Add composable wrapper only if required by domain behavior
4. Add new primitive only when no existing primitive can satisfy requirements

## Consistency Rules

- Prefer shared spacing and typography rhythm used by existing pages/layouts
- Keep component APIs minimal, typed, and composable
- Avoid one-off style islands; align with tokens/presets
- Keep primitives behavior-light and app wrappers behavior-rich

## Interaction Rules

- Every interactive control has hover + focus-visible styles
- Motion is subtle and purposeful (avoid noisy animation)
- Visual feedback for async actions is mandatory
